Business Analyst

Any Technology is a Singapore-based banking IT solutions provider, powering international financial institutions with deep fintech expertise and our revolutionary proprietary technology. As we continue to expand globally, we are looking for IT professionals to join our Thailand office and grow together with the company.




Job Responsibilities:

1.     Responsible to collect and analysis of business requirements of the credit card core system and related peripheral systems, sorting out business processes, and providing solutions;

2.     Responsible for product prototype and functional design based on business analysis results;

3.     Responsible for connecting with internal product R&D personnel, relevant customer personnel and project delivery support, including but not limited to program planning, analysis and system design, progress control, system testing, online support, etc.;

4.     Responsible for writing relevant product design, analysis and detailed design documents;

5.     Obtain feedback from different users in the process of using the system in time, promote product optimization and improvement, and improve user experience.




Job Requirements:

1.     Bachelor’s degree or above, computer related professional background is preferred;

2.     A minimum of 5 years of experience in credit card business requirement analysis and writing, or consumer credit related business demand analysis and product design experience;

3.     Experience in credit card core system testing, development and product related work is preferred

4.     Have strong logical thinking ability, communication ability and written expression ability, can quickly understand business requirements and form relevant documents;

5.     Proficient in using demand research auxiliary stools, such as Visio, PPT, Axure, XMind, etc.;

6.     Quick learning, good sense of responsibility and pressure resistance.
